    <para>A <emphasis role="bold">Verified</emphasis> Guest OS has been tested by HPE and appears to function properly as a
        Nova compute virtual machine on [[[kw-hos-phrase]]].</para>
<para>A <emphasis role="bold">Certified</emphasis> Guest OS has been officially tested by the operating system vendor, or
        by HPE under the vendor's authorized program, and will be supported by the operating system
        vendor as a Nova compute virtual machine on [[[kw-hos-phrase]]].</para>
